  "dialogues": [
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "多谢你提醒我，我的确不是你妈妈的对手。",
      "tone": "阴损"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "你，你，居然会使太极剑法！",
      "tone": "震惊"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "好，你把更厉害的使出来吧！",
      "tone": "挑衅"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "你莫笑痛我的肚皮了。",
      "tone": "刻薄"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "不错，我是不该骂你的妈妈，我是骂那负心人！",
      "tone": "怨毒"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "杀你爹爹的不是我，杀你娘亲的也不是我，你冤魂不舍地缠住我干什么？",
      "tone": "急辩"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "你的剑法是不是妈妈教的？",
      "tone": "质询"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "line": "妖妇，知道历害了么！知道厉害的在后头呢！",
      "tone": "佯狂"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "line": "小鬼你有多大，也要避嫌。",
      "tone": "嗔怪"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "line": "你那姐姐都叫我做姐姐呢，你说你应该叫我做什么？",
      "tone": "得意"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "line": "表哥是和你一起的，你知不知道他去哪儿？",
      "tone": "急切"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "妈，不知怎么搞的，我也好像是脑袋沉重的很，气力都使不出来了。",
      "tone": "慌张"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "贼秃休得伤我娘亲！",
      "tone": "急怒"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "我不屑嫁给他，凤姐，你的好意我心领了。",
      "tone": "倔强"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "line": "莫说一条手臂，你有本事，要我这条性命也可以！",
      "tone": "刚烈"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "line": "他们不会自己检吗？",
      "tone": "羞恼"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "我和你姐姐是同年同月同日生的，已经十七岁了。",
      "tone": "实诚"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "凡事都不例外，爹爹说我像舅舅，姐姐像妈妈，那又有什么稀奇。",
      "tone": "勉强"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "你不是也有一个表哥吗？",
      "tone": "无心"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "老话说得好，吉人天相。你也无需太过担心，牟师叔他会逢凶化吉的。",
      "tone": "安慰"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "我不知道此地是否有武功比那蒙面人更高的人，但我知道是早已有人帮他的了。",
      "tone": "安慰"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "是个燕字。",
      "tone": "试探"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "真诚"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "剑诀是师祖传的，招式是我义父所教，不过我也胡乱想出一些新招。",
      "tone": "实诚"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "慧可大师曾点过我，不过他和我说的乃是武学精义，不是剑法。",
      "tone": "实诚"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "请恕我不能回山替师祖送葬，我有事要先走。",
      "tone": "坚定"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "这件事是师祖生前嘱咐我的，请怨我不能假手别人。",
      "tone": "坚定"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "listener": "char_ji_cuo",
      "line": "大和尚，你还是趁早给自己念往生咒吧！",
      "tone": "冷嘲"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "别慌，娘在这儿！",
      "tone": "慈爱"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "line": "你们不要骂他，他这号人，是把'人不为己，天诛地灭'奉作金科玉律的",
      "tone": "不屑"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "line": "陆志诚，你下毒的本事高明得很呀，居然瞒过了我！",
      "tone": "冷峻"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "listener": "char_jin_ding_he",
      "line": "你们要人，就给你们的人！",
      "tone": "嘲讽"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "走乾转巽，金鼓雷鸣。",
      "tone": "指点"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "listener": "char_han_chao",
      "line": "你不是主谋，死罪可免，活罪难饶。",
      "tone": "严正"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "转离方，走巽，反臂刺扎！",
      "tone": "指点"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "line": "好，那我倒要问你了，你因何下毒害我？",
      "tone": "质询"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "listener": "char_lai_bao_er",
      "line": "来保儿，你也要改换门庭？好，那就来吧，我成全你！",
      "tone": "威严"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "line": "唐二先生好吗？他放心让你一个人出来，倒是难得。",
      "tone": "佯狂"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_yong",
      "line": "你只配做龟儿子！",
      "tone": "怒骂"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "干娘，我可不想勉强你。",
      "tone": "关切"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_lan_yu_jing",
      "line": "哦，胡乱想的？你倒是聪明得紧啊！",
      "tone": "酸讽"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "我的事虽没办好，也总算有了一点收获。",
      "tone": "无奈"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_jin_ding_he",
      "line": "我是想见七星剑客，可不想见你们的可汗！",
      "tone": "刚烈"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_jin_ding_he",
      "line": "我既非贤士也非侠土，不过我是汉人，不是汉奸！",
      "tone": "愤慨"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "你救过我的性命，这解药给你，从今以后，谁也不欠谁的。",
      "tone": "决绝"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "我是为了赎罪！",
      "tone": "冷峻"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "你知道我的妈妈是怎么死的吗？",
      "tone": "恨意"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "不要我对我好，你也别指望我忘了是你害死我的母亲！",
      "tone": "决裂"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "我不要你对我好！",
      "tone": "决裂"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_ji_cuo",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "你的功夫不错呀，怎的交手一招就跑了。",
      "tone": "轻佻"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_ji_cuo",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "听说你的丈夫早死了，你无依无靠，也是可怜，你给佛爷做个女弟子吧！",
      "tone": "调笑"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_qi_zhen_jun",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "我是来为自己的弟兄挽回过失，不知牟少侠因何反加拦阻？",
      "tone": "傲然"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_jin_ding_he",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "西门夫人莲驾江临，请恕有失远迎。",
      "tone": "客气"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_jin_ding_he",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "夫人你太嫌了。敝国大汗，求材若渴，只要是个人才，大汗用人是不问出身的。",
      "tone": "圆滑"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_jin_ding_he",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "姑娘，昨晚之事我可以不计较，今日这件事情，我肯罢休，只怕弟兄们也不心服。",
      "tone": "威胁"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_jin_ding_he",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "牟少侠，你和我们结下的梁子，我们可以算了。但蓝玉京曾经杀伤我们好几位兄弟。",
      "tone": "威胁"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_jin_ding_he",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "郭老前辈，这里可有人要见你呢！",
      "tone": "恭敬"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_han_chao",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "夫人请莫误会，他是要来的，只不过……",
      "tone": "赔笑"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_han_chao",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "他并不敢自高身价，我托他去向金鼎和疏通。",
      "tone": "恭顺"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_han_chao",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "金老板正有此意，……要不要上京一趟。",
      "tone": "建议"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "参见盟主夫人。",
      "tone": "恭顺"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "奔走之责，这是属下份所当办，怎敢望夫人酬报？",
      "tone": "恭顺"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "金鼎和表面是鱼行老板，其实他的官职比快马韩还高。",
      "tone": "揭秘"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "夫人你看怎样？",
      "tone": "请示"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "西门姑娘，你别怪我直话直说，你想牟一羽回来，只怕是除非做梦了！",
      "tone": "威胁"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "阴间秀才就是要靠这些本事立足的。",
      "tone": "阴险"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "我本来是要倚仗夫人做靠山的。但夫人你却不肯帮我的忙。",
      "tone": "坦白"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "金鼎和已经答应我，只要我把你们母女缚送给他，他一定可以帮我在可汗跟前说话。",
      "tone": "坦白"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "好小子，两人打一个算得什么好汉，有胆的出来与我再战！",
      "tone": "虚张"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_ping_da_shen",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "line": "陆志诚，没想到你竟是这样狠心狗肺！",
      "tone": "怒骂"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_ping_da_shen",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "line": "夫人有何亏待你？",
      "tone": "质问"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_feng_qi_wu",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "line": "陆舵主，你有何倚恃，胆敢如此欺侮夫人？",
      "tone": "质问"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_feng_qi_wu",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "line": "放走夫人，你要什么，我都可以答应你。",
      "tone": "诱降"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_feng_qi_wu",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "line": "我愿意嫁给你。",
      "tone": "献媚"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "妈，牟大哥解药真灵，我的武功已经恢复啦。",
      "tone": "兴奋"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "line": "做鞑子的鹰爪，是不是比狗都不如？",
      "tone": "怒骂"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_feng_qi_wu",
      "line": "嫁猪嫁狗都胜嫁给他，凤姐，你的好意我心领了。",
      "tone": "刚烈"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhi_cheng",
      "line": "你要杀便杀，何必多言。",
      "tone": "刚烈"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "妈，你好像什么都知道。",
      "tone": "狐疑"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "我是说，你对牟大哥的事情，好像知道得比我还多。",
      "tone": "狐疑"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "我看！那就是说，你确是还有别的事情了。",
      "tone": "追问"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "妈，我一百个愿意。实不相瞒，我也想见一见我那干妹子呢。",
      "tone": "欢快"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_qi_xing_jian_ke",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "只许我说。不许你问！",
      "tone": "威严"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_qi_xing_jian_ke",
      "listener": "char_mou_yi_yu",
      "line": "我能够告诉你的只是，嗯，别怪我说话不够客气，令尊虽然不是什么正人君，但也不至于堕落到做别人的帮凶。",
      "tone": "直率"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_qi_xing_jian_ke",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_fu_ren",
      "line": "物换星移几度秋，那堪重为故人留。",
      "tone": "感慨"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_hui_ke",
      "listener": null,
      "line": "佛曰：不可说。不可说！",
      "tone": "佛偈"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_hui_ke",
      "listener": null,
      "line": "生死原是转法轮，又何必在人间再留下解不开、理还乱的仇冤？",
      "tone": "佛偈"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_hui_ke",
      "listener": null,
      "line": "这孩子，可是我看着他长大的啊！",
      "tone": "慈爱"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yong",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "你叫我一声老子，我就饶你！",
      "tone": "狂妄"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yong",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "line": "常五娘，你当真是只要小白脸不要朋友了吗？",
      "tone": "质问"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_ying_song_ling",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_yan",
      "line": "又来你这小子！",
      "tone": "恼怒"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_ying_song_ling",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_niang",
      "line": "小子，我要你的命！",
      "tone": "凶狠"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_ying_song_ling",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_yong",
      "line": "让他们多嘴多舌。",
      "tone": "命令"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_ying_song_ling",
      "listener": "char_han_chao",
      "line": "你少担心，嘉错法师的修罗散你当是寻常的蒙汗药么？",
      "tone": "安抚"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_ying_song_ling",
      "listener": "char_han_chao",
      "line": "看这位西门夫人，武学已废，你怕什么？",
      "tone": "鼓劲"
    },
    {
      "chapter": 14,
      "speaker": "char_lai_bao_er",
